## 🌟 Key Features

- **Smart Financial Engine:** Calculate gross/net revenue, remove sales tax automatically, project real take-home profits.
- **Inventory & Waste Tracking:** Log inventory items and costs to control food cost percentages.
- **Labor + Overtime Automation:** Calculate labor cost, including built-in 1.5x overtime logic after 8 hours per shift.
- **Global Recipe Library:** Standardize recipes and food costing across all units, with a global database of menu items.
- **Multi-Location/Unit Support:** Seamlessly manage unlimited branches, audit performance, and aggregate results.
- **Daily Trend Analysis:** Visualize daily/weekly net profits with bar charts and history tracking.
- **Secure and Private:** Local data storage (with export/import options) keeps your information safe and in your hands.
- **Report/Export Tools:** Generate PDF audits, CSV data dumps, and JSON backups/restores with one click.
- **Master Dashboard:** View a global roll-up of ALL your locations’ performance at a glance.

