## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Open the App
- Download or clone this repository.
- Open `index.html` in any modern web browser.

### 2. Authentication
- Enter your secure access key to unlock the dashboard.

### 3. Basic Workflow  
- Input daily gross sales, taxes, and overhead.
- Add inventory purchases and labor/staff entries.
- Track profit margins in real time.
- Use the recipe calculator to standardize food costs across your brand.

---

## 📦 Installation (Advanced/Hosting)

1. Fork or clone this repo.
2. Open `index.html` directly *(no build step required)*.
3. To deploy on GitHub Pages:
   - Go to **Settings > Pages** in your repository.
   - Set source to `main` branch, `/ (root)`.
   - Your business dashboard will be live at  
     `https://restologicllc.github.io/restologic-enterprise-os/`.

